== Transaction Coordinator ==
The TC module provides the two phase commit coordination functionality for [[OpenDaylight_Virtual_Tenant_Network_(VTN):VTN_Coordinator|VTN coordinator]] components.
It consists of two subcomponents
:*[[#Transaction_Coordinator|Transaction Coordinator (TC)]]
:*[[#Transaction_Coordinator_Library|Transaction Coordinator Library (TCLIB)]]

